event: response.output_text.done
data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_cc4dd94a60f900880069cc468bc6148190beffd309eac7ace7","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":286,"text":"The Contoso Galaxy Innovations line includes cutting-edge products such as Smart Eyewear designed for enhancing daily life with advanced technology. Key details about one of its products, the \"SmartView Glasses,\" are as follows:\n\n### Features of Contoso SmartView Glasses:\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: Offers immersive digital overlays to enhance real-world experiences.\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: Enables hands-free operation for seamless use and smart interactions.\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Ensures high-quality recordings supported by spatial sound capabilities.\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Protects eyes during extended use, beneficial for both indoor and outdoor environments.\n5. **Wireless Charging and Extended Battery Life**: Provides convenience with long runtimes and efficient power management.\n\n### Additional Information:\n- **User Friendly Design**: Sizing and fit adjustment guides help users find their optimal comfort.\n- **Safety and Maintenance**: Includes tips for safe use in various spaces, cleaning procedures, and care instructions.\n- **Warranty**: Comes with a two-year limited warranty covering electronic components.\n- **Return Policy**: Contoso offers a generous 30-day return period without questions.\n\nFor assistance or more details, Customer Support can be contacted via their email at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com."}

