data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_cc4dd94a60f900880069cc4693a3b081908952217fa58fab1b","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":300,"text":"The Smart Eyewear offered by Contoso Galaxy Innovations includes innovative features designed to enhance modern lifestyles. Here are the key features of their flagship product, the **SmartView Glasses**:\n\n### Features of Smart Eyewear:\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: Enables immersive and interactive digital overlays on real-world environments.\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: Facilitates hands-free operation and communication with integrated intelligence.\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Offers impressive recording capabilities with spatial sound for dynamic playback.\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Ensures user eye safety during prolonged usage.\n5. **Wireless Charging and Extended Battery Life**: Provides convenience and reliability for long-term use.\n\n### Support and Maintenance:\n- **Sizing and Fit**: Includes adjustable options to suit user preferences for comfort.\n- **Safety Tips**: Published guidelines for usage in both public and private spaces.\n- **Product Care**: Recommendations for cleaning and maintenance ensure durability.\n\n### Additional Information:\n- **Warranty**: Includes a two-year limited warranty covering electronic components.\n- **Return Policy**: Offers a 30-day return option with no questions asked.\n- **FAQ**: Contains details on device synchronization, connection troubleshooting, and customization of augmented reality features.\n\nFor more details or inquiries, Contoso's Customer Support is reachable at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com."}

